{
  "texts": [
    "We write a Python script to randomly create, modify and delete files in the monitored directory.",
    "As a result, the FIM module generates logs and forwards them to SIEM whenever a change is detected in the directory.",
    "This methodology is used for OSSIM, Wazuh, and SIEMonster.",
    "In the case of Elastic Security, the Auditbeat agent is installed in the Ubuntu and Windows systems.",
    "Inside Auditbeat, the path for the directories that need to be monitored for changes is configured."
  ]
}